data.description: Charming MidMod home in heart of Shadow Mountain! Featuring 3 beds and 2 baths, full loft offers many options for second living, office, game or movie room, sky’s the limit!! Tall ceilings, spacious rooms and great entertaining spaces are perfect for all. You’ll love the new granite countertops, and the cost efficiency & peace of mind that come with a NEW Roof & NEW HVAC! Circle drive & extra parking spaces are perfect for this corner lot & enjoy the outdoor covered patio for exterior living. Great for families, entertaining or even an investment property for AirBNB options! You have to seem this gem of a home!
